---
export const prerender = true;
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — HisaabKar.pk"
  description="Privacy policy for HisaabKar.pk — Pakistani finance tools and economic analysis platform."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">Last updated: March 19, 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-gray dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>HisaabKar.pk ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and your rights regarding your data when you use our website at <strong>hisaabkar.pk</strong>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">2a. Automatically Collected Data</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>IP address and general location (country/city level)</li>
          <li>Browser type and version</li>
          <li>Pages visited and time spent</li>
          <li>Referring website</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">This data is collected via <strong>Cloudflare Web Analytics</strong>, which is privacy-friendly and does not use cookies or fingerprinting.</p>

        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 mt-4">2b. Calculator Inputs</h3>
        <p>All financial calculations (tax, salary, zakat, loan, etc.) are performed <strong>entirely in your browser</strong>. Your financial data is never sent to our servers or stored anywhere.</p>

        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 mt-4">2c. Document Converter</h3>
        <p>Files uploaded for conversion via our Document Converter are processed by <a href="https://cloudconvert.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-green-600 underline">CloudConvert</a> (a third-party service). Files are automatically deleted from CloudConvert servers within 24 hours. Image-to-PDF conversion runs entirely in your browser — no file is uploaded.</p>

        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 mt-4">2d. Newsletter</h3>
        <p>If you subscribe to our newsletter, we collect your email address solely to send economic updates. You can unsubscribe at any time via the link in any email.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">3. Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use minimal cookies:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Theme preference</strong> (localStorage) — stores your dark/light mode choice</li>
          <li><strong>No tracking cookies</strong> — we do not use Google Analytics, Facebook Pixel, or other tracking services</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">We use <strong>Google AdSense</strong> to display advertisements. Google may use cookies to serve ads based on your visits to this and other websites. You can opt out via <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-green-600 underline">Google Ad Settings</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">4. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>To provide and improve our financial tools and economic content</li>
          <li>To send newsletters (only if you subscribed)</li>
          <li>To monitor site performance and fix errors</li>
          <li>To display relevant advertisements via Google AdSense</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">We do <strong>not</strong> sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — CDN, DNS, analytics, and hosting. <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-green-600 underline">Privacy policy</a></li>
          <li><strong>CloudConvert</strong> — Document conversion. <a href="https://cloudconvert.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-green-600 underline">Privacy policy</a></li>
          <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong> — Advertising. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-green-600 underline">Privacy policy</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">6. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain analytics data for up to 90 days. Newsletter email addresses are retained until you unsubscribe. Document conversion files are deleted from CloudConvert within 24 hours.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Access any personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Unsubscribe from our newsletter at any time</li>
          <li>Opt out of Google AdSense personalised ads</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:ashfaqahmed1192@gmail.com" class="text-green-600 underline">ashfaqahmed1192@gmail.com</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">8. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Our services are not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the top reflects the most recent revision. Continued use of the site constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">10. Contact</h2>
        <p>For privacy-related queries:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Email: <a href="mailto:ashfaqahmed1192@gmail.com" class="text-green-600 underline">ashfaqahmed1192@gmail.com</a></li>
          <li>Website: <a href="https://hisaabkar.pk" class="text-green-600 underline">hisaabkar.pk</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
